{"about_the_game":"Battle Clash is a medieval multiplayer PVP game. On spawn, each player is randomly assigned a medieval class and forced to battle against other players. Reach a kill streak to unlock your class's ultimate attack, and dominate the battlefield. When the timer ends, the player with the most kills wins!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785480/extras/gif1-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1708185307\" /><br><br>There are 8 medieval classes in the game, and they each have <strong>their own unique set of skills:</strong><br><br>Knight<br>Primary: Sword slash<br>Secondary: Defensive Shield Block<br>Ultimate: Blitz (faster movement, and attack speed)<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785480/extras/knighticon.png?t=1708185307\" /><br><br>Heavy<br>Primary: Battleaxe Bludgeon<br>Secondary: Quick Dash<br>Ultimate: Rage (increased damage, and movement speed)<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785480/extras/heavyicon.png?t=1708185307\" /><br><br>Archer<br>Primary: Bow &amp; Arrow Shot<br>Secondary: Bow Shove<br>Ultimate: Ruthless (sees through walls, and increased arrow damage)<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785480/extras/archericon.png?t=1708185307\" /><br><br>Wizard<br>Primary: Spell Cast<br>Secondary: Staff Shove<br>Ultimate: Fireball (well, it's a fireball. A deadly fireball)<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785480/extras/wizardicon.png?t=1708185307\" /><br><br>Spearman<br>Primary: Spear Thrust<br>Secondary: Defensive Spear Spin<br>Ultimate: Impale (throws spear at enemy, typically one-shotting anyone)<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785480/extras/spearmanicon.